[{"from": "human", "value": "Can you demonstrate how to set up the bounce settings with a code snippet?"}, {"from": "gpt", "value": "Certainly! Here's a basic code example of how to set up and store SMTP bounce settings configuration in PHP for LimeSurvey:

```php
